Package: hydroscoper
Type: Package
Title: R interface to hydroscope
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Konstantinos", "Vantas", email = "kon.vantas@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Konstantinos Vantas <kon.vantas@gmail.com>
Description: R interface to the  Greek National Data Bank for Hydrological and 
    Meteorological Information, [Hydroscope](<http://www.hydroscope.gr/>). It 
    covers most of Hydroscope's sources and provides functions to transform 
    these untidy data sets into tidy dataframes.
URL: https://github.com/kvantas/hydroscoper
BugReports: https://github.com/kvantas/hydroscoper/issues             
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
